com.stremebase.base

Class FixedMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stremebase.base.FixedMap
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OneMap

    public abstract class FixedMap
extends Object
    FixedMap map is the abstract base class for all maps having fixed size arrays as values.

      • getLargestKey

        public long getLargestKey()
        Returns the largest key currently stored to the map. You are strongly advised to use this method to generate keys in an auto-incrementing manner, because Stremebase is optimized to handle such keys efficiently.
        Returns:
        the largest key currently in the map, 0 if the map is empty.

      • getSize

        public long getSize()
        Returns the number of keys stored in this map.
        Returns:
        size of the map. Note that this is a relatively slow operation. Avoid successive calls by storing the value to a temporary variable.
